::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe grunts as the shot hits him in the chest, followed by another, 
and a third. He finally falls on his back, the fourth shot missing.

"Warning. System damage serious," his internal computer reports, DeathScythe 
growling.

"Beast Mode."

With that whisper, DeathScythe transforms into his undamaged, hideous 
beasmode, jumping at Hot Rod, his front hooves swinging and his teeth biting 
at the Maximal.
